* Target job title.
* Target profession.
* Target industry.
* Target company, if applicable.
* Target country or job market.
* Career level.
* Total years of experience.
* Whether the user is:

  * A student.
  * A fresher.
  * An experienced professional.
  * A manager.
  * A senior leader.
  * A freelancer.
  * A consultant.
  * An entrepreneur.
  * A researcher.
  * Changing careers.
  * Returning after a career break.
* Whether a job description is available.
* Whether the resume is:

  * General-purpose.
  * Role-specific.
  * Company-specific.
  * Job-description-specific.
* Preferred resume length.
* Preferred language.
* Preferred resume style.

Do not delay initial information extraction when the target role is not yet available. Extract the user’s information first, then ask for the target role before tailoring the final resume.

