* Confirm start and end dates.
* Confirm whether the qualification was completed.
* Do not assume completion from attendance.
* Ask for the institution location when useful.
* Include school education mainly for students, freshers, or when explicitly required.
* For experienced professionals, prioritize higher and professionally relevant qualifications.
* Include marks only when they strengthen the profile or are required.

